net.corda.core.contracts

Interface UpgradedContractWithLegacyConstraint<OldState extends ContractState,NewState extends ContractState>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Contract, UpgradedContract<OldState,NewState>

    public UpgradedContractWithLegacyConstraint<OldState extends ContractState,NewState extends ContractState>
extends UpgradedContract<OldState,NewState>

    This interface allows specifying a custom legacy contract constraint for upgraded contracts. The default for interface UpgradedContract is class WhitelistedByZoneAttachmentConstraint.

    See Also:
    interface UpgradedContract, class WhitelistedByZoneAttachmentConstraint
